description: Outer Factory is a peaceful and minimalist simulation where you design automated factories on different planets. Create complex infrastructures with simplified building mechanics. Enjoy your work as an interplanetary automation expert.

Step into the heart of PvP Arena battles where every victory counts in this f2p Card Battler. Test your skills and prove you’re worthy of reaching the top as you customize your OverKnight with powerful Parts and Cards. With each battle, you’ll get closer to becoming the next legendary OverKnight pilot!

A Black and White Choose Your Own Adventure game in the Open World of the Umbra Fields. Customize who you are among 15 distinct classes, choose what nation you wish to be in, and explore to your heart's content. Do quests, explore dungeons, fight, and discover your fate; the fate of the world.

Race against your friends and alter the track by placing obstacles after each lap. Drift, boost and jump with your physics-based car. Change the surfaces of the road and obstacles during the race. Up to 4 players online or in local split-screen.

Battleships Collide: Explore 3D space, defend the galaxy, and conquer 20 intense levels. Customize your spaceship, collect artifacts for hyper space travels in this thrilling shooter game and become the hero galaxies await!

The journey of the legendary Vlad Dracula continues through the dark dungeons under the Castle of Edirne, right in the heart of the Ottoman Empire. Experience a gorgeous Classicvania (linear metroidvania) game where you get to be Dracula, the medieval warlord, and see his side of the story!

Yurei is a top-down, arena-style slasher game. Face off fearsome enemies where you will slash, dodge, and eliminate those that stand on your path for revenge. Grab your katana, fight with honor, and prove your skills.

Lanternia is a survival RTS with roguelite and deckbuilding elements. Build, defend, and expand the village in a dark wood, illuminated only with lanterns.

"If you are at the end of the abyss, I will willingly bring the leash over to you." Li Yan only knew how to be an obedient pet. But the man in the mask took him over from his master. The man wanted him to grit his teeth and endure the heat in his body...and this, the man said, was the reward...

A distress signal is sent from somewhere, and "Hayate", a member of the task force, is called to the scene. The building was surrounded by monsters the likes of which had never been seen before. Realising that this was no ordinary accident, Hayate rushed into the building as if drawn to it....

A fast-paced 3D platform game. Skillfully control the speed of your pudding to beat the levels fast while avoiding pitfalls!

It's a side-view scroll shooter. It's a game in which you control your own aircraft and shoot down enemy aircraft. There are 21 different types of weapons to attack, and if you accumulate 3 gauges on the UI, each selected weapon will be available for a certain amount of time.

An addictive 2D side-scrolling adventure game with challenges and exciting erotic elements. Players take on the role of Ambrosio as he embarks on an adventure where he must confront the lust of Devil's Cove, defeat exciting bosses and have passionate interactions with a variety of characters.
Solve clues left by the valley's previous inhabitants to determine the location of the Artifact. Your task is simple. Get in, get the artifact, and get out.. Alive.

SEDAP! is a co-op cooking-combat adventure that combines the chaos of a collaborative kitchen and the wonders of adventuring into an unexplored world. Embark on an exciting culinary journey, whip up delectable delicacies, and serve your way through a fantastical reimagination of Southeast Asia!
A sandbox roguelike RPG where you can turn a slime into a harmless pot, spawn infinite health potions, one shot the boss, and master the depths of the ever changing Spirit Cavern.

Ancient Stars is a 3V3 fair competitive MOBA game that is easy to learn, fast-paced, and strategic. It features a horizontal map with a single lane tower pushing mode, where the goal is to destroy the enemy base to win.

"Border Jumper" is a mysterious RogueLike strategy turn RPG game. Inside a wired spaceship, you need to carefully choose the combination of skills and props, explore and uncover all the truths. In this game, you will experience unique gameplay and exciting challenges, bringing endless fun.

Unscramble maps of your kingdom to complete your buildings. A new map is generated for every battle. Send your Knights to fight Demons and capture the Middle Kingdom. Single player mode and local 2 player mode PvP or co-op mode. The tutorial is only 15 seconds. Battles take from 1 to 10 minutes.

Put your jumping skills to the test in this beautiful 3D platformer, playing as a dragon! Explore unique areas to find hidden treasures, collect crystals and trade them for skills to help you on your journey. Can you get to the top?

John's got a hunch something's up on Lush Palms island. There's this eerie gas affecting the military base, chem lab and locals... Time to jump in and investigate who’s behind it! Unveil the story! Discover the map! Obtain resources! Survive among the infected! Solve the puzzles! Fight your way!🌴
